            </div>

            <div class="box" data-aos="flip-left">
                <img src="img/caurse3.jpg" alt="">
                <h3 class="caurseheading">civil Engineering</h3>
                <p>Civil engineering is a professional engineering discipline that deals with the design, construction,
                    and maintenance of the physical and naturally built environment, including public works such as
                    roads, bridges, canals, and railways.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="box" data-aos="flip-right">
                <img src="img/caurse4.png" alt="">
                <h3 class="caurseheading">bachelors in computer application</h3>
