            </div>

            <div class="box" data-aos="flip-down">
                <img src="img/caurse5.jpg" alt="">
                <h3 class="caurseheading">bachelors of business administration</h3>
                <p>BBA is one of the most popular and sought after bachelor degree programmes pursued by students after Class 12. The BBA course is the gateway to a plethora of job opportunities in numerous sectors such as Marketing, Education, Finance</p>
            </div>

            <div class="box" data-aos="flip-up">
                <img src="img/caurse6.jpg" alt="">
                <h3 class="caurseheading">master of business administration</h3>
